{
  "stem": "11175.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So you saw, every day, dying, and dying, from that-- from that hunger.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they didn't have what to eat.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I was a king.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I had a piece of bread and a little soup.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I gave it to friends also.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we-- I was there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we went to the shop every morning.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was no more Taunton barrack.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What were you making in the shop?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What were you doing?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All kind of carpentry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They-- that-- now, that-- but the end, we realized that they made the coffers, you know?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Boxes to prepare themself to put in everything in the boxes and to take out from there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You see?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they had their belongings, and the belongings from the-- from the-- from the lager, from the camp.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, they were close with the other camp, you know?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Ukrainians were close with the other one, that you-- there's gold.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and-- and-- everything was laying on the-- in the-- in the Treblinka where they burned them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were on the ground.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Which area?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Lanz.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Lanz, that's right.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One day, before I-- I-- one-- this is very characteristic-- one day, we went out to [NON-ENGLISH], work the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Coming back from work was a sturmfuher there with the name-- we called him the [NON-ENGLISH], the [NON-ENGLISH] A older man.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was an older man.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now, he was a completely murderer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If you-- you-- you don't-- you cannot understand it, you know?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You-- he-- he-- when you-- you hear this-- I told this in the front of the court also, whenever I was called to-- We came back from work, and we went into the camp, not the-- outside.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this-- he was standing outside.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
